title: James Walsh (Starsailor) 2009-03-12 - The Deaf Institute, Manche
description:
James Walsh (Starsailor) 2009-03-12 - The Deaf Institute, Manchester, UK



An XFM Manchester Broadcast, recorded and split into individual MP3 files. James Walsh(lead singer) and his guitar performing tracks from Love Is Here, Silence Is Easy and their new album All The Plans in the small, intimate Deaf Institute in Manchester, UK.
